descr:
Recognizing Anagrams

Question 1. Define a function anagrams of type string -> string -> bool such that anagrams s1 s2 returns true if and only if the strings s1 and s2 are anagrams of one another.

Hint Two strings are anagrams of one another if and only if they have the same histogram, that is, the same number of occurrences of every character.
Hint Use some of the functions in the standard library modules `String` and `Map`.
